body_text: How Jade Mills Reigns as #1 Global Agent for Coldwell Banker THE GOAL Gain greater brand recognition within one of the world’s most prestigious real estate markets. Built a beautiful website that tells Jade’s story Created blog posts to showcase Jade’s market expertise Elevated the experience for website visitors with thoughtful design Helped create a powerful personal brand, enhancing trust and authenticity “People always tell me how beautiful my site is, and my clients love how beautifully their properties are displayed.
